room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms in Princeton
room_description: Our local police department is so short staffed they are calling for volunteers to assist with a nasty crime scene.  Watch out, though, for the WICKED plot twist!   Not for the feint of heart, this room is a horror based room and may not be suitable for young children.  Come join us, if you have the courage, for a series of twists, scares and craziness!
